<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>微表情识人术 - 完整版电子书</title>
<style>
*{
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}
body{
    background-color: #1E80FF;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: "微软雅黑",sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    line-height: 2.2;
}
.title-box{
    margin: 40px 0;
}
.title-box h1{
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}
.title-box p{
    font-size: 20px;
    opacity: 0.9;
}
.desc-box{
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto 50px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    padding: 30px 25px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    font-size: 18px;
}
.desc-box h3{
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 22px;
}
.qr-box{
    background: #ffffff;
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    margin-bottom: 60px;
}
.qr-box img{
    width: 220px;
    border-radius: 10px;
}
.qr-tip{
    color: #333;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 16px;
}
.footer{
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    font-size: 14px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="title-box">
    <h1>微表情识人术</h1>
    <p>完整版高清电子书 · 一眼看透人心</p >
</div>

<div class="desc-box">
    <h3>本书介绍</h3>
    <p>语言可以伪装，微表情无法隐藏</p >
    <p>零基础快速掌握眼神、眉眼、嘴角、肢体识人技巧</p >
    <p>适用于职场、社交、人情、恋爱、做生意谈客户</p >
    <p>全书完整章节，排版清晰，可永久保存随时阅读</p >
    <p>完整版PDF仅付费专属获取</p >
</div>

<div class="qr-box">
    < img src="qrcode.png" alt="扫码付费购买">
    <div class="qr-tip">扫码支付，付款后联系我发送完整电子书</div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
© 2026 河北龙杰启明传媒 版权所有
</div>

</body>
</html> 
